Moving in
When you’re moving in to your student apartment, you can pick your keys up at our Bobutik in downtown Falun. Before getting the keys to your apartment, we have to receive your payment for the first rent. You can pay the first rent with your credit card directly in our Bobutik. Remember to bring approved ID (e.g. passport). You can pick your keys up after 12:00 pm on the first day in each month (not Saturdays or Sundays). Our Bobutik on Stigaregatan 3 B is open Mon-Fri between 10 am-5 pm.
